tagline: Qt Widget Factory, a bit like awf just for Qt widgets
name: qwf
body:
# qwf
## is a widget factory for Qt widgets

qwf (NOT Qwf or QWF) is a widget factory a bit like awf. It is for people to test out what themes look like in Qt, or use this in KDE (on Linux) to test out KDE themes.
